{"tid":2011590,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［Twitter國際戰線］學習日本尋日到底點樣將一個Hashtag推到當地#1甚至全球#5","createTime":"2020-05-11T06:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T19:04:28.000Z","uid":137653,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0efd62ef8a4b114c2a5a67c30a322676d6878847","tid":2011590,"uid":137653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:03:17.000Z","msg":"第一次開po，如果有咩不足歡迎指教指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋日日本Twitte trends #1嘅係 #検察庁法改正案に抗議します，今日凌晨1點已經有超過470萬則投稿，甚至一度推到全球嘅#5。<br />\n而今日個Hashtag已經冇係日本Twitter trends出現，疑似係俾人清除緊推文阻止討論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/spkwkRz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FspkwkRz.jpg&h=bfaeca9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2wziDf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2wziDf.jpg&h=0529eef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuUtocA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuUtocA.png&h=00f4c64f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n      <br />\n由於重點唔係討論法案損害三權分立嘅議題，焦點會集中係到底日本網民點樣推po推上#1。<br />\n有人甚至認為如果將依啲200萬個tweet係現實可視化嘅話，尋日係喺日本進行緊相當於香港200萬人上街規模嘅示威抗議。 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNjw5ie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNjw5ie.jpg&h=58c386c1&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n日本網民嘅做法：<br />\n-做推文bot<br />\n用五十音或者英文字母加Hashtag無限推po，達到人海戰術嘅效果<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oZ7q9KW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZ7q9KW.jpg&h=74fd421f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n-融入日常生活（唔代表推到變習以為常/麻木）<br />\n其實依樣都相當重要，一黎可以推到po，二黎令大家唔會忘記仲未達到目標，抗爭同生活兩樣同時進行係毫無衝突<br />\n當然有小動物更加吸引人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F5YmH9k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF5YmH9k.png&h=33e2682f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Ak0YHF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Ak0YHF.png&h=38305e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 推唔起就要及時止蝕，再推起另外一個tag<br />\n今日就到釣魚臺問題，佢地亦將推唔到嘅#検察庁法改正案に抗議します一齊出po希望可以推得翻上去，希望大家都關注兩個重要嘅話題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sey59Xx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSey59Xx.png&h=a292a74f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ugdt7Kc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fugdt7Kc.png&h=d84c682d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然有啲地方香港冇辦法學習嘅係日本唔少嘅藝能界/知名人士都有出聲抗議，例如小泉今日子、生物股長嘅水野良樹、きゃりーぱみゅぱみゅ、伊藤潤二、奈良美智等等。<br />\n佢地發聲除咗能夠影響關注佢地嘅人，同時都會引起公眾輿論，報章都會加以報導<br />\n反觀之下香港得清一色奶共藝人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好似きゃりーぱみゅぱみゅ咁，有人讚賞佢作為公眾人物都勇敢發聲，亦都有人表示失望，覺得作為歌手唔好亂講野，好好唱歌好過，而最後都係因為輿論同歌手身份最後都係跪咗將言論除去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEkcPUE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEkcPUE.png&h=475f79a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S8zQByS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS8zQByS.png&h=44985185&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/duJmJdS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FduJmJdS.png&h=08234429&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"021f34c0af68aa6d1112f28ffaef1a2414b92388","tid":2011590,"uid":125502,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"d3e6db9682e092942c770bdaac781342fe5a1918","tid":2011590,"uid":137653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:05:14.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e720c53e162020b327030780920d582cb2a3334","tid":2011590,"uid":137653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3e6db9682e092942c770bdaac781342fe5a1918","tid":2011590,"uid":137653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:05:14.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:05:36.000Z","msg":"再輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba4a7cd967dfd462683ba6ef6cd606987c02815","tid":2011590,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:07:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沈日有傻仔話寫bot 推文<br />\n但要引用作者來源</span>"},{"pid":"35cb1fe28c127552cb12897573442e60a730893d","tid":2011590,"uid":137653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ba4a7cd967dfd462683ba6ef6cd606987c02815","tid":2011590,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:07:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沈日有傻仔話寫bot 推文<br />\n但要引用作者來源</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:08:36.000Z","msg":"意思係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e321c02f9c50035af832640c6d6cb6e21c5c08d0","tid":2011590,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:10:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10f4e27482011c46d0062670b79d8c4970f7c2bb","tid":2011590,"uid":49018,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime"